Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安！…真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家來做客  你要做個乖孩子哦
