Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般沒這樣的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來實現你的願望吧
