Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  出發囉～小鏡也快上來上來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不上
