Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.22,0:38:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.08,0:38:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.11,0:38:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會閃過去的  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.07,0:38:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人員最喜歡晶小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.48,0:38:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.27,0:38:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.30,0:38:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  誰拿份水來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.18,0:38:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人員給我水  給我水
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.53,0:38:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.42,0:38:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.02,0:38:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.00,0:38:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.39,0:39:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢  等到她心情好為止
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.52,0:39:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微有點渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.81,0:39:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想喝點水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.56,0:39:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.26,0:39:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Staf～f～{\r}\N工作人猿～
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.26,0:39:13.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（搞笑藝人狩野英孝的拿手段子之一，不過不包括“人猿”= w =）
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.73,0:39:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Staf～f～{\r}\N工作人猿～
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.16,0:39:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也給我來點水
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.04,0:39:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Staf～f～{\r}\N工作人猿～
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.68,0:39:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.15,0:39:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.64,0:39:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  為什麼把麥克風拿掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.69,0:39:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.03,0:39:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水呢  水…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.44,0:39:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人猿…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.66,0:39:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.46,0:39:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.51,0:39:43.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.51,0:39:43.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（本回幸運頻道主題歌為「愛をとりもどせ」，北斗神拳的OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.71,0:39:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.49,0:39:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.99,0:39:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.51,0:39:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.04,0:39:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是說了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.19,0:39:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這不對勁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.34,0:39:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.37,0:39:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.63,0:40:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對勁啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.55,0:40:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.66,0:40:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.88,0:40:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.71,0:40:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想學乖了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.05,0:40:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀唉呀  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.52,0:40:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之呢  我一直想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.86,0:40:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是會讓我上正片上正片
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.23,0:40:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻完全沒我的戲份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.33,0:40:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺我剛流行起來
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.14,0:40:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流行就過時了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.83,0:40:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我都說了正片裡只要是個角色我都演的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.66,0:40:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.54,0:40:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  晶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.49,0:40:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會有好事的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.97,0:40:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果呢…那啥啊…愛不夠啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.64,0:40:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶小姐  結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.10,0:41:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  已經要結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.45,0:41:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶好寂寞～
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.38,0:41:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.78,0:41:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.77,0:41:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  新的地址
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.59,0:41:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這附近  這附近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.77,0:41:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把滿滿的愛送給晶
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.82,0:41:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請期待著下次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.88,0:41:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  再見～
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.04,0:41:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見～
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.23,0:41:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的  會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.41,0:41:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.78,0:41:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意忘形就是這樣  夜露死苦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.20,0:41:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嗎啊  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.15,0:41:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.59,0:41:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.66,0:41:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.54,0:41:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意忘形到無法收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.79,0:41:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.40,0:41:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.86,0:41:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點再得意下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.44,0:41:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再得意下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.80,0:41:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直得意下去  然後就
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.40,0:41:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆地
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.14,0:41:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆地
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.01,0:41:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆地那麼一下子
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.80,0:41:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆地解決  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.91,0:41:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「乾脆」也得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.66,0:42:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒把握  我努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.16,0:42:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.61,0:38:30.47,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YouはShock　愛で空が落ちてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.85,0:38:36.66,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YouはShock　俺の胸に落ちてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.03,0:38:43.10,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱い心　クサリでつないでも　今は無駄だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.34,0:38:49.32,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪魔する奴は指先ひとつで　ダウンさ
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.49,0:38:55.47,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YouはShock　愛で鼓動早くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.80,0:39:01.57,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YouはShock　俺の鼓動早くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.90,0:39:08.19,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お前求め　さまよう心　今　熱く燃えている
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.30,0:39:14.76,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全て溶かし　無残に飛び散るはずさ
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.16,0:39:21.91,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺との愛を守る為　お前は旅立ち
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.22,0:39:28.01,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日を　見うしなった
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.29,0:39:34.43,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微笑み忘れた顔など　見たくはないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.71,0:39:40.47,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛を取り戻せ…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.61,0:38:30.47,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You將Shock　天空因愛而下落
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.85,0:38:36.66,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You將Shock　於我的胸中下落
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.03,0:38:43.10,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火熱的心　即便用鎖鏈相連　現已無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.34,0:38:49.32,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡是阻擋我的傢伙　用一根手指將其Down掉
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.49,0:38:55.47,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You將Shock　心中的鼓動因愛提前到來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.80,0:39:01.57,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You將Shock　我的鼓動也因此提前到來
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.90,0:39:08.19,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求著你　彷徨的心　如今炙熱地燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.30,0:39:14.76,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要將一切融化　慘不忍睹地四散飛濺
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.16,0:39:21.91,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了守護與我的愛　你踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.22,0:39:28.01,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失了明日的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.29,0:39:34.43,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看到你那忘記微笑的臉龐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.71,0:39:40.47,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來找回我們的愛吧…


